en comment\\\">// Your custom options</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"token comment\\\">// see: https://fancyapps.com/fancybox/api/options/</span>\\n   <span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">}</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n  </span></span><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre><p><br></p><p><strong>The order is important!</strong></p><p><br></p><p>I know that a whole series of files have to be included.&nbsp;</p><p>But...</p><p>The implementation of the <em>page-o-builder</em> is quite simple.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>2. Implement the</strong> <span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">&lt;page-o-builder&gt;</span><span style=\\\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">&lt;/page-o-builder&gt;</span> </span><span style=\\\"color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><strong>and the output / preview</strong></span><span style=\\\"color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); color: rgb(192, 80, 77); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\\\">&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"> </span><span style=\\\"color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><strong>tag</strong></span><span style=\\\"color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><pre class=\\\"language-html\\\"><code class=\\\"language-html\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span>\\n\\n    <span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>page-o-builder</span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">container</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>container<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">output</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>.preview-output<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">is-frissbee-player</span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">no-data</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>page-o-builder</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span>\\n\\n    <span class=\\\"token comment\\\">&lt;!-- the output / preview HTML element --&gt;</span>\\n    <span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">class</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>preview-output<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span> <span class=\\\"token special-attr\\\"><span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">style</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span><span class=\\\"token value css language-css\\\"><span class=\\\"token property\\\">display</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">:</span> none<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span></span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span></span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre><p><br></p><p>The&nbsp;<span style=\\\"background-color: transparent; font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">&lt;page-o-builder&gt;</span><span style=\\\"background-color: transparent; color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">&lt;/page-o-builder&gt;</span></span><span style=\\\"background-color: transparent; color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">&nbsp;tag has 4 attributes:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\\\">container</span> =&gt;&nbsp; for YOUR container CSS wrapper class</li><li><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\\\">output</span> =&gt; class name or id of the output / preview HTML element</li><li><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\\\">no-data</span> =&gt; When a <u>new page</u> is created (meaning no data is loaded) the attribute \\\"<span style=\\\"color: rgb(149, 55, 52); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\\\">no-data</span>\\\" must be set.&nbsp;A value does not have to be specified.&nbsp;<u>If data is loaded, this attribute must be removed</u></li><li><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\\\">is-frissbee-player</span> =&gt; If the FrissBee Audio Player is implemented, this attribute must be specified.&nbsp;A value does not have to be specified.</li></ul><p>The output area for the preview is therefore not integrated in the <em>page-o-builder</em>&nbsp;so that you can implement the integration according to your own ideas.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>3. The database</strong></p><p>The data of a created page must be stored persistently in a database.</p><p>The <em>page-O-builder</em> needs 2 columns in a database table:</p><ul><li>for the editor data (contentEditor) and</li><li>for the data of the page (contentPage)</li></ul><p>There is a sample database in the repo.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>4. Save the data in the Database</strong></p><p>To save the data, you get the data via the&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); color: rgb(192, 80, 77); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\\\">getContent()</span><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">&nbsp;function as object: <span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">{ contentEditor: [data], contentPage: [data] }</span>.</span></p><p>Example:</p><pre class=\\\"language-js\\\"><code class=\\\"language-js\\\"><span class=\\\"token keyword\\\">const</span> pageBuilder <span class=\\\"token operator\\\">=</span> document<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">querySelector</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token string\\\">\'page-o-builder\'</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n<span class=\\\"token keyword\\\">const</span> data <span class=\\\"token operator\\\">=</span> pageBuilder<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">getContent</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n\\nconsole<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">log</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token string\\\">\'Content Editor\'</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">,</span> data<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span>contentEditor<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\nconsole<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">log</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token string\\\">\'Content Page\'</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">,</span> data<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span>contentPage<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"token comment\\\">// Your function to save a new page</span>\\n<span class=\\\"token function\\\">insertData</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token constant\\\">JSON</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">stringify</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span>data<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span>contentEditor<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">,</span> data<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span>contentPage<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"token comment\\\">// Your function to save an existing page</span>\\n<span class=\\\"token function\\\">saveData</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token constant\\\">JSON</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">stringify</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span>data<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span>contentEditor<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">,</span> data<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span>contentPage<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">,</span> idContents<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span></code></pre><p><br></p><p><strong>5. Edit an existing page</strong></p><p>To edit a page stored in the database, the data must be queried from the database and then transferred to the <em>page-o-builder</em>.</p><p>How you query the data is entirely up to you.&nbsp;<span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">There is a sample in the repo.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">You can transfer the data to the <em>page-o-builder</em> with the <span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">setContentEditor()</span> function.</span></p><p>Example:</p><pre class=\\\"language-js\\\"><code class=\\\"language-js\\\"><span class=\\\"token keyword\\\">const</span> pageBuilder <span class=\\\"token operator\\\">=</span> document<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">querySelector</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token string\\\">\'page-o-builder\'</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"token keyword\\\">const</span> contentEditor <span class=\\\"token operator\\\">=</span> <span class=\\\"token function\\\">yourFunctionToGetThe_contentEditor_DataFromTheDatabase</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n\\npageBuilder<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">setContentEditor</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span>contentEditor<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span></code></pre><p>The <span style=\\\"color: rgb(149, 55, 52); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\\\">contentPage</span> data does not need to be transferred to the <em>page-o-builder</em>, as the <em>page-o-builder</em> generates it from the <span style=\\\"color: rgb(149, 55, 52); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\\\">contentEditor</span> data.</p><p><br></p><h5 style=\\\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\\\">Displaying the created page content</h5><h5 style=\\\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 16px;\\\">1.&nbsp;Implement all files</span></h5><p>In the&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;</span>&nbsp;tag:</p><pre class=\\\"language-html\\\"><code class=\\\"language-html\\\"><span class=\\\"token comment\\\">&lt;!-- optional: fancybox --&gt;</span>\\n<span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">src</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fancyapps/ui@5.0/dist/fancybox/fancybox.umd.js<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\\\"token script\\\"></span><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">rel</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">href</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fancyapps/ui@5.0/dist/fancybox/fancybox.css<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">/&gt;</span></span>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"token comment\\\">&lt;!-- otional: FrissBee Audio Player --&gt;</span>\\n<span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">src</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>./your-path-to-the-file/frissbee-audio-player_1.0.3.js<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\\\"token script\\\"></span><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"token comment\\\">&lt;!-- the page-o-builder file for the responsive design. --&gt;</span>\\n<span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">src</span><span class=\\\"token attr-value\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation attr-equals\\\">=</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span>./your-path-to-the-file/page-o-builder.show-page.v0.1.0.js<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">\\\"</span></span> <span class=\\\"token attr-name\\\">defer</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\\\"token script\\\"></span><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre><p><br></p><p>After the&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">&lt;body&gt;&lt;/body&gt;</span>&nbsp;tag:</p><pre class=\\\"language-html\\\"><code class=\\\"language-html\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\\\"token script\\\"><span class=\\\"token language-javascript\\\">\\n    <span class=\\\"token comment\\\">// optional: fancybox</span>\\n    <span class=\\\"token function\\\">Fancybox</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">bind</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token string\\\">\'[data-fancybox]\'</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">,</span> <span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">{</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"token comment\\\">// Your custom options</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"token comment\\\">// see: https://fancyapps.com/fancybox/api/options/</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">}</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">;</span>\\n  </span></span><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token tag\\\"><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre><p><br></p><p>It is entirely up to you to query the data and display it on the page.</p><p>There is a simple example in the repo. Customize it according to your wishes.</p><p><span style=\\\"color: var(--bs-body-color); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight);\\\"><br></span></p><h5 style=\\\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\\\">A few words about some of the editors</h5><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><strong>Text editor</strong></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">The <em>page-o-builder</em> uses the Trumbowyg WYSIWYG text editor.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">If you only want to use the basic options of the text editor, leave out the&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"background-color: initial; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: inherit; word-spacing: normal; white-space: pre; font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight);\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">trumbowyg.plugins.min.js</span></span><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight);\\\">&nbsp;file.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">More information about the <a href=\\\"https://alex-d.github.io/Trumbowyg/\\\" title=\\\"https://alex-d.github.io/Trumbowyg/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Trumbowyg editor can be found here</a>.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><strong>Image editor</strong></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">With the image editor you have three options:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">Insert image</span></li><li><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">Insert image that can also be used as a link</span></li><li><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">Show image in a lightbox when you click on it</span></li></ul><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">The fancybox is used for the lightbox.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">You can find more information about the <a href=\\\"https://fancyapps.com/fancybox/api/options/\\\" title=\\\"https://fancyapps.com/fancybox/api/options/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">fancybox, including the configuration, here</a>.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">Without configuration, the fancybox is used in full mode, i.e. the way it is usually used anyway.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">The implementation of the fancybox is optional.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\"><strong>FrissBee Player</strong></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">The FrissBee Audio Player can be used to have more options when integrating an audio file than with the standard audio player.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">More information about the <a href=\\\"https://audio-player.frissbee.de/\\\" title=\\\"https://audio-player.frissbee.de/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">FrissBee Audio Player can be found here</a>.</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\">The implementation of the FrissBee Player is optional.</span></p><p><br></p>\",\"orderCell\":\"1\",\"cellBackgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"cellBackgroundImg\":\"\",\"cellPadding\":\"0\",\"cellCssClass\":\"\",\"cellCssStyle\":\"width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; text-wrap: wrap; word-wrap: break-word; \"}],\"columnWidth\":\"100\",\"columnBackgroundImg\":\"\",\"columnBackgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"columnPadding\":\"0\",\"columnCssClass\":\"\",\"columnCssStyle\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; \"}]},\"rowBackgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"rowBackgroundImg\":\"\",\"rowPadding\":\"0\",\"rowCssClass\":\"\",\"rowCssStyle\":\"width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; \",\"rowGap\":\"40px\"}]', '<style>.pob-d-flex-1014-wgstzux { display: flex; } @media screen and (max-width: 992px) { .pob-d-flex-1014-wgstzux { display: block; } }</style>\n                  <div\n                    class=\"\"\n                    style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; \">\n                    <div class=\"container\">\n                      <div class=\"pob-d-flex-1014-wgstzux\" style=\"width: 100%; gap: 40px; padding: 0;\">\n                      <div\n                        class=\"pob-container-screen-resize-wgstzux \"\n                        style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; padding: 0; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; \"\n                      >\n                          <div\n                            class=\"\"\n                            style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; padding: 0; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; text-wrap: wrap; word-wrap: break-word; \"\n                          >\n                            <h4>Documentation</h4><p><br></p><p>Let\'s make it as simple as possible.</p><p>Go to the GitHub page and clone or download the repo:</p>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div\n                    class=\"\"\n                    style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; \">\n                    <div class=\"container\">\n                      <div class=\"pob-d-flex-1014-wgstzux\" style=\"width: 100%; gap: 40px; padding: 0;\">\n                      <div\n                        class=\"pob-container-screen-resize-wgstzux \"\n                        style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; padding: 0; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; \"\n                      >\n                          <div\n                            class=\"\"\n                            style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; padding: 0 0 20px; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; text-wrap: wrap; word-wrap: break-word; \"\n                          >\n                            <div id=\"btn-container\" style=\"text-align: left\">\n                          <a href=\"https://github.com/FrissBee/page-o-builder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" custom-target=\"_blank\">\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-dark\" style=\"\" custom-style=\"\">GitHub</button>\n                          </a>\n                        </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div\n                    class=\"\"\n                    style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; \">\n                    <div class=\"container\">\n                      <div class=\"pob-d-flex-1014-wgstzux\" style=\"width: 100%; gap: 40px; padding: 0;\">\n                      <div\n                        class=\"pob-container-screen-resize-wgstzux \"\n                        style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; padding: 0; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; \"\n                      >\n                          <div\n                            class=\"\"\n                            style=\"background-image: url(\'\'); background-color: transparent; padding: 0; width: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: cover; text-wrap: wrap; word-wrap: break-word; \"\n                          >\n                            <p>The repo contains all the necessary files and a simple example of how to implement the <em>page-O-builder</em> in your own site.</p><p>Basically, that was it.</p><p>Everything is explained in more detail below.</p><p><br></p><h5>Description</h5><p>There are two basic scenarios:</p><ul><li>working with the page builder to create or update a page</li><li>displaying the created page content</li></ul><p><br></p><h5>Working with the page builder to create or update a page</h5><p><strong>1.&nbsp;Implement all files</strong></p><p>In the <span style=\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\">&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;</span> tag:</p><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- optional: fancybox --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fancyapps/ui@5.0/dist/fancybox/fancybox.umd.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fancyapps/ui@5.0/dist/fancybox/fancybox.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;\n</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- otional: FrissBee Audio Player --&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token pu